\par\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 Instruments used in post-mortem examinations should never be employed for operating upon the living, without first being repolished by the instrument maker, and the handles disinfected by careful cleaning in a solution of permanganate of potash.}{ }
