\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 Life is already at work consuming the moment one has died.  Putrefaction is a byproduct of life.}
\par\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b1 Notes.}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~In all important cases, notes should be taken down by an assistant, on the spot, as dictated by the operator; heading these by the name and age of the patient and a brief sketch of the disease. In medico-legal cases, this is to be conducted with particular care, as will be pointed out hereafter.}{ }
